latestPosts.caption:
One of my early memories of the musical “The Phantom Of The Opera “ was that of mystique and love! ❤️ 🎭🎻🎶
Based on a 1910 novel by Gaston Leroux, The Phantom of the Opera tells the tale of a disfigured musical genius who haunts the Paris Opera House. Mesmerised by the talents and beauty of the young soprano Christine, the Phantom lures her as his protégé and falls fiercely in love with her. ❣️🫶
Ive been obsessed with this musical for years because of top notch performances and the live singing by all the actors on stage! 
Also, im guilty of being obsessed with the songs of this absolute masterpiece by Sir Andrew Lloyd Webber! A true masterpiece! And a must watch for all the theatre and musical fans! 💯😘🎭🎶🧑‍🎤🎷🎻
Thank you @nmacc.india for brining it to India! Loved every but of  @phantomopera @phantomoftheopera with my partner in everything @shivanikumrafitness 👯‍♀️💪😘❤️🎭

Cannot wait to have their power stories on our podcast @curtaincallstories 💫❤️🎭

Wearing my beautiful outfit @raahjaipur
